==English==
===Noun===
'''Responsibility'''
#A. The [[act]] of being [[responsible]]
#* '''Responsibility''' is a heavy burden
#B. [[duty]] or [[obligation]] for which someone is responsible
#* Keeping this system under control is everyone's '''responsibility'''
#C. A [[liability]] that you must take care of
#* Why didn't you clean the house?!? You were '''responsible''' for that!!
